<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/113000033/2025-26/evaluation> a ns1:EvaluationSystem ;
    ns1:evaluationDescription """ASSESSMENT and EVALUATION
Progressive assessment and compulsory attendance in a 75%
Grammar test
Report on a research article (report format)
Paper on analysis of abstracts (research article format)
Face-to-Face Classes

Final global exercise that will include :
- Use of academic vocabulary
- Write the different parts of a research article (Abstract, Results part, etc.)
- Use of grammar in Research Articles (common errors),"""@es .

